dc_title_s: Replication data for: Labour Force Survey (LFS) - Archive data
dc_description_s: Data is no longer available for dissemination. If you require access to these files for reference purposes, please contact your library's Data Liberation Initiative liason.   Series collection of LFS data files.These data represent LFS data prior to the official process of rebasing for latest population statistics (2006 Census). These data are no longer disseminated through Statistics Canada, or the Data Liberation Initiative (DLI). Rebased data is available through ODESI, see: http://odesi.ca
